'''齧齒動物'''也称作'''啮形大目'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|Glires}}），是咬食性[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]的总称，包含了[[齧齒目|齧齒目]]和[[兔形目|兔形目]]等[[演化支|演化支]]。其中齧齒目的代表动物有[[松鼠|松鼠]]、[[河狸|河狸]]、[[鼠|鼠]]、[[豪猪|豪猪]]等，兔形目的代表动物有[[家兔|家兔]]、[[野兔|野兔]]和[[鼠兔|鼠兔]]等。<ref>{{cite book|author1=郑智民|title=啮齿动物学|date=2008|location=上海交通大学出版社}}</ref>

==物种==
[[File:Mammalia-percent-schinese.png|缩略图]]
<!--[[File:Rodent_species_pie_chart.png|thumb]]有2/3的物種屬於[[鼠總科|鼠總科]]。其中，[[鼠科|鼠科]]（藍：Muriade）和[[倉鼠科|倉鼠科]]（紅：Cricetidae）構成了[[鼠總科|鼠總科]]的絕大部份。]]-->
對齧齒動物是一個[[單系群|單系群]]的假定，長久以來都存在著很大的爭議，儘管最近的形態學研究強烈地支持齧齒動物是單系群的<ref>Meng, J., and A.R. Wyss, 2001. The morphology of ''Tribosphenomys'' (Rodentiaformes, Mammalia): phylogenetic implications for basal Glires. ''Journal of Mammalian Evolution'' 8(1):1-71.</ref><ref name="meng2003">*Meng J., Y. Hu, C. Li, 2003. The osteology of ''Rhombomylus'' (Mammalia, Glires): implications for phylogeny and evolution of Glires. ''Bulletin of the American Museum of Natural History'' 275:1-247. [http://hdl.handle.net/2246/442]</ref>。新的[[化石|化石]]發現填補了齧齒目和兔形目之間的裂縫<ref name="meng2003" /><ref>Asher R.J., J. Meng, J.R. Wible, M.C. McKenna, G.W. Rougier, D. Dashzeveg, and M.J. Novacek, 2005. Stem Lagomorpha and the antiquity of Glires. ''Science'' 307:1091-1094. [http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/307/5712/1091 Abstract] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/abstract/307/5712/1091 |date=20091010043631 }}</ref>。[[細胞核|細胞核]]DNA的資料支持齧齒動物是[[靈長動物|靈長動物]]的旁系群，且兩者組成[[靈長總目|靈長總目]]<ref>Madsen O., M. Scally, C. J. Douady, D. J. Kao, R. W. DeBry, R. Adkins, H. M. Amrine, M. J. Stanhope, W. W. de Jong, M. S. Springer, 2001 Parallel adaptive radiations in two major clades of placental mammals. ''Nature'' 409:610-614. [http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=retrieve&db=pubmed&list_uids=11214318&dopt=Abstract]</ref><ref>Murphy W. J., E. Eizirik, W. E. Johnson, Y. P. Zhang, O. A. Ryder, S. J. O'Brien, 2001a. Molecular phylogenetics and the origins of placental mammals. ''Nature'' 409:614-618.  [http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/query.fcgi?cmd=retrieve&db=pubmed&list_uids=11214319&dopt=Abstract]</ref>，但有些從細胞核和[[粒線體DNA|粒線體DNA]]得出的基因資料卻對此論點較少支持<ref>Ulfur Arnason, et al. Mammalian mitogenomic relationships and the root of the eutherian tree. ''Proceedings of the National Academy of Science'' 99: 8151-8156. [http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/full/99/12/8151] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pnas.org/cgi/content/full/99/12/8151 |date=20080517115137 }}</ref>。一份對[[逆轉位子|逆轉位子]]存在/消失的研究則無疑地支持了齧齒動物的假定<ref>Jan Ole Kriegs, Gennady Churakov, Jerzy Jurka, Jürgen Brosius, and Jürgen Schmitz (2007) Evolutionary history of 7SL RNA-derived SINEs in Supraprimates. Trends in Genetics 23 (4): 158-161 [http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.tig.2007.02.002] (PDF version {{cite web |url=http://zmbe2.uni-muenster.de/expath/articles/31_Kriegs_TiG.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2007-04-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070803072737/http://zmbe2.uni-muenster.de/expath/articles/31_Kriegs_TiG.pdf |archivedate=2007-08-03 }})</ref>。根據分子學的研究成果，齧齒動物在靈長總目內的亲缘關係可能是：
{{灵长总目支序分类法}}

世界上啮齿动物的种类或个体数量可能比其他所有哺乳动物加起来还要多，啮齿动物包括：[[海狸|海狸]]、[[花栗鼠|花栗鼠]]、[[老鼠|老鼠]]、[[豪猪|豪猪]]以及[[松鼠|松鼠]]等<ref>{{cite web|title=啮齿动物|url=http://www.bowenwang.com.cn/animals-rodent.htm|website=博闻网|accessdate=2016-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031213642/http://www.bowenwang.com.cn/animals-rodent.htm|archive-date=2016-10-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[水豚|水豚]]是世界上最大的啮齿类生物，原產於[[南美洲|南美洲]]的稀樹草原和叢林中<ref name=msw3>{{MSW3 Woods|id=13400218|page=1556}}</ref><ref name="inDarwin">{{Cite book | last=Darwin | first=Charles R. | year=1839 | title=Narrative of the surveying voyages of His Majesty's Ships Adventure and Beagle between the years 1826 and 1836, describing their examination of the southern shores of South America, and the Beagle's circumnavigation of the globe. Journal and remarks. 1832–1836. | place =London | publisher =Henry Colburn | page=619}}</ref>。

==特征==
[[兔形目|兔形目]]与[[啮齿目|啮齿目]]一样都有可以不断生长的[[门齿|门齿]]，没有[[犬齿|犬齿]]，其生活习性也和典型的啮齿目比较相似<ref>{{cite web|title=兔型目Lagomorpha|url=http://old.hssyxx.com/zhsj/kexue-2/zutiweb/zu31/013/00-2.htm|accessdate=2016-10-31|archive-date=2017-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170108064954/http://old.hssyxx.com/zhsj/kexue-2/zutiweb/zu31/013/00-2.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不同的是[[囓齒目|囓齒目]]上下顎各只有一對門齒，而[[兔形目|兔形目]]则有2對上門齒<ref>{{cite web|title=老鼠是囓齒目動物|url=http://www.nmns.edu.tw/public/exhibit/2008/97-2-mouse/completed/com-2.htm|website=国力自然科学博物馆|accessdate=2016-10-31|date=2008-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101041055/http://www.nmns.edu.tw/public/exhibit/2008/97-2-mouse/completed/com-2.htm|archive-date=2016-11-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

